caption: Come join us this Wednesday, 6-10pm, for another night of gaming in Wilson Hall!

In addition to our regular board game night we're hosting a JACKBOX GAME NIGHT Friday the 13th from 6-8pm!

We have officially partnered up with JackBox Games and will be giving out Game Keys for JackBox Games as Prizes for the Event! 

Jackbox Games will be ran in two rooms, WILSON HALL ROOM 2002 and 2007D from 6 pm- 8 pm. There will be two computers hosting 3 games each over the span of 2 hours (each game hosts around 6 people). NO SIGN UP NEEDED, FIRST COME FIRST SERVE

We will also have board games on the side while you are waiting for your turn in Jackbox, so if you just want to play some board games or just chill, you can come and treat this as a normal board game night. (the room is still booked from 6pm - 10pm)

Hope to see you all there!

Join us this Wednesday 6-10pm in Wilson Hall room 2002 for another board game night! 
Come again if you were there last week or drop in for the first time this week, everyone is welcome!
